"```sql\nSELECT account.account_id\nFROM account\nJOIN loan ON account.account_id = loan.account_id\nWHERE loan.date LIKE '1997%' \nAND loan.amount = (SELECT MIN(amount) \n                   FROM loan \n                   WHERE date LIKE '1997%' \n                   AND account_id IN (SELECT account_id \n                                      FROM account \n                                      WHERE frequency = 'POPLATEK TYDNE'));\n```"